DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260723T190000
DTSTAMP:20260723T131400Z
UID:gz-2026-business-after-hours-at-renasant-bank-1663881@southbaldwincham
 ber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nRenasant Bank\nis proud to partner with\nRapahope
  Children’s Retreat Foundation\nfor this special Business After Hours ev
 ent!\nGive your business a boost by attending Business After Hours and net
 work with your fellow Chamber members and business owners. Chamber members
  most often do business with other chamber members\, so bring a stack of y
 our business cards and get ready to talk shop in the laid-back atmosphere 
 that Business After Hours provides. Of course\, there will be plenty of so
 cializing and great food\, too.\nNot only is Business After Hours a great 
 way to make new contacts and build your referral list\, but you will also 
 likely find a service provider there that you have been looking for\, as w
 ell. South Baldwin Chamber events are mutually beneficial and prove to be 
 an excellent way to build relationships with others in our business commun
 ity.\nJoin us for an evening of networking\, connection\, and community im
 pact with\nRenasant Bank\nand\nRapahope Children’s Retreat Foundation\n!
 \nCatering provided by The Tin Top Restaurant and Oyster Bar\nNo registrat
 ion required!\n*Members Only Event*\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: http
 s://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/2026-business-aft
 er-hours-at-renasant-bank-1663881
LOCATION:Renasant Bank\, 1207 N McKenzie Street\, Foley\,\, AL\, 36535\, U
 nited States
END:VEVENT
