BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:MT Jones at OWA Theater
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260916T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260916T210000
DTSTAMP:20260723T131400Z
UID:gz-mt-jones-at-owa-theater-1776167@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nCatch UK soul artist MT Jones live at OWA Theater
  on September 16\, 2026!\nWhile in town for Americana Fest 2026\, MT Jones
  is making a handful of special performances\, and OWA Theater is one of t
 hem! With smooth vocals\, heartfelt lyrics\, and a sound that blends class
 ic soul with a modern edge\, this is your chance to experience an artist o
 n the rise in an intimate live setting.\nDoors open at 6:00 PM.\nAbout MT 
 Jones\nGathering inspiration from 60s and 70s soul greats across the Atlan
 tic to modern R&B and jazz\, MT Jones evokes a sound that is both contempo
 rary and timeless. His deeply soulful vocals transport you straight back t
 o a smoke-filled speak easy which somehow still feels fresh and innovative
 .\nBetween stints working on music regularly in Liverpool & London\, Jones
  has travelled the world as a musician & penned songs for other artists\, 
 making a name for himself as a gifted and prolific songwriter.\nSince then
 \, lockdown gave him the time and space to put his talent under his own na
 me. His debut single ‘I Won't Ever Say Goodbye’ is a soulful\, heart-o
 n-sleeve ballad that marks the start of big things & his latest single ‘
 Feeling Lonely’ has quickly followed suit. He has received great support
  from BBC\, introducing multiple spins on 1xtra\, a ‘Step up’ artist o
 n the show. He has also enjoyed strong playlist support from Spotify inclu
 ding several New Music Friday adds in the UK.\nThis is only the start for 
 this highly memorable and distinctive singer\, song writer\, musician and 
 creator!\nGrab your tickets today!\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https
 ://businesshub.southbaldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/mt-jones-at-owa-th
 eater-1776167
LOCATION:OWA Theater\, 205-A N OWA Boulevard\, Foley\,\, AL\, 36535\, Unit
 ed States
END:VEVENT
