 53@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nSince 1976\, the South Baldwin Chamber of Commerc
 e has been celebrating the spirit of the Free Enterprise system by awardin
 g the\nWalton M. Vines Free Enterprise Person of the Year\n. This award is
  presented by\nRiviera Utilities\nand is one of South Baldwin's most covet
 ed awards.\nTo be nominated\, a person must still be active in business af
 fairs\, have a good moral reputation\, be active in civic and community af
 fairs\, and be committed to helping others grow. The winner is honored dur
 ing the Free Enterprise Person of the Year Luncheon at the Foley Civic Cen
 ter\, which is attended by more than one hundred of the area's top busines
 s leaders and community members.\nThe Luncheon features a full catered mea
 l and speeches from the previous year's winner along with the newly honore
 d Person of the Year. You are invited to join us for this prestigious even
 t!\nView Event Webpage\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https://businessh
