BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Foley Main Street Third Thursdays
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260709T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260709T190000
DTSTAMP:20260723T131400Z
UID:gz-foley-main-street-third-thursdays-1848856@southbaldwinchamber.com
DESCRIPTION:Description\nWhile the traditional holiday season may still be
  months away\,\nFoley Main Street\nis proving it’s never too early for a
  little festive cheer. On Thursday\, July 16th\, Downtown Foley will be op
 en for a special “Christmas in July” Third Thursday event.\nAs shopper
 s increasingly look to get a head start on their holiday lists\,\nFoley Ma
 in Street\nis leaning into the trend by turning its monthly Third Thursday
  into a great opportunity to get started early. This July celebration mark
 s the beginning of a new tradition for the downtown district\, Christmas i
 n July.\n“We all know people are starting their Christmas shopping earli
 er and earlier\, so we thought\, why not July?” said Darrelyn Dunmore\, 
 Executive Director of Foley Main Street. “We’re inviting everyone to c
 elebrate the season with a summer twist—think tropical vibes\, cool drin
 ks\, and a very special guest from the North Pole. We want to give people 
 a reason to explore our beautiful downtown\, support our local shops\, and
  have a little mid-summer fun without the stress of the actual holiday rus
 h.”\nFor more information about the Christmas in July Third Thursday eve
 nt\, please visit\nwww.foleymainstreet.com\nor follow Foley Main Street on
  social media.\n\n---\n🌐 View original event: https://businesshub.south
 baldwinchamber.com/calendar/Details/foley-main-street-third-thursdays-1848
 856
LOCATION:Downtown Foley\, Foley\,\, AL\, 36535\, United States
END:VEVENT
